            <lg xml:id="TK951">
<l>ilpiṟantār kaṇṇalla tillai yiyalpākac </l>
<l>ceppamu nāṇu moruṅku</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Consistency (of thought, word and deed) and fear (of sin) are conjointly natural only to the high-born.</l>
